" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Insertion of soft tissue dilator for central venous catheter placement",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 273px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The soft tissue dilator is advanced over the guidewire using a corkscrew motion. Mild resistance is normal. The dilator does NOT need to be advanced its entire length, but only to the anticipated depth of the vessel.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
