"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block mop drugH1Div\" id=\"F182627\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Monitoring Parameters",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Monitor response (pain, range of motion, grip strength, mobility, ADL function), inflammation; observe for weight gain, edema; monitor renal function (serum creatinine, BUN); observe for bleeding, bruising; evaluate gastrointestinal effects (abdominal pain, bleeding, dyspepsia); mental confusion, disorientation, CBC, liver function tests (particularly with pediatric use); ophthalmologic exams with prolonged therapy",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
