"     Adapted from Jankovic, J, Fahn, S. Dystonic disorders. In: Jankovic, J, Tolosa, E, (Eds), Parkinson's disease and movement disorders, 3rd ed, Williams &amp; Wilkins, Baltimore 1998. p. 513.",
"    </div>",
